'''何家慧'''（'''{{lang-en|Eva Ho}}'''），[[香港|香港]]前女演員，1973年畢業于第二期[[無綫電視藝員訓練班|無綫電視藝員訓練班]]，1970年代中後期于無綫電視劇集及《[[歡樂今宵|歡樂今宵]]》中演出。1978年加入樂壇推出個人大碟《小白船》<ref>[https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BaFKLr9PBvgMkVlOgkXIdJ&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc 何家慧得意歌壇 不想重回電視台] {{Wayback|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BaFKLr9PBvgMkVlOgkXIdJ&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%B6%E6%85%A7%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc |date=20200708034126 }} [[工商日報|工商日報]]. 1978-11-30</ref>，1988年曾以部頭形式簽約[[亞洲電視|亞洲電視]]演出電視劇<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_